criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age between 18-80 years;

          -  ST segment elevation myocardial infarction (STEMI);

          -  Plan to primary percutaneous coronary intervention.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Age more than 80;

          -  renal failure with creatinine >2 mg/dl;

          -  reject taking part in the study.
